track.name: Nature Boy
comments: The greatest thing, you'll ever learn...
The track, is the mood I seek as a time to reflect.  Definitely a must have in an OUTSTANDING library.  His music, at times for me has been the catylist to improving my own creativity.

Great. Elvin is just laying those brushes down like no other, and Mingus is really hot on this. Truly great.
This is my favorite song of all time. Perfect!
